dataset.title: Description of Xiphinema karachiense sp. n. and morphometric data on Enchodelus macrodorus (de Man, 1880), Thorne, 1939 (Nematoda: Dorylaimida) from Pakistan

abstract.para: This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article NASlRA, Kazi, Firoza, Kazi, Maqbool, Mohammad A. (1992): Description of Xiphinema karachiense sp. n. and morphometric data on Enchodelus macrodorus (de Man, 1880), Thorne, 1939 (Nematoda: Dorylaimida) from Pakistan. Fundam. appl.
